title: 259. Andy & DJ CTI: Twitter Suspends Babylon Bee, Sen. Hawley Warns Of Biden's SCOTUS Pick & Hunter Biden's Laptop
itunes:title: 259. Andy & DJ CTI: Twitter Suspends Babylon Bee, Sen. Hawley Warns Of Biden's SCOTUS Pick & Hunter Biden's Laptop
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ discuss Twitter suspending Babylon Bee's account after posting Rachel Levine as "Man of the year," Senator Hawley warning of Biden's SCOTUS pick which shows a record of letting child porn offenders off the hook and the mainstream media finally admitting Hunter Biden's laptop is real.
